	('It was great','Rất tuyệt','00:04:36.140','00:04:36.860','dhar-mann-studio-1'),
	('Oh, and I found a new song for us to dance to','À, con đã tìm được một bài hát mới để chúng ta nhảy rồi','00:04:37.360','00:04:39.400','dhar-mann-studio-1'),
	('I\'ll teach you when we get home','Con sẽ dạy bố khi chúng ta về nhà','00:04:39.560','00:04:40.620','dhar-mann-studio-1'),
	('That sounds great, sweetie','Nghe tuyệt đấy, con yêu','00:04:41.220','00:04:42.120','dhar-mann-studio-1'),
